---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 34
  - Title: Mânava-dharma-sâstra
    Chapter:
      - I
      - Verse: 80
Tags:
  - Creation=Creation as Play or Sport
---
Manvantaras are countless, as are also the creations and destructions;
the Supreme Being does this again and again as if in sport.
